# get_irida_download_sequence_pair
# download both R1 and R2 files for a paired-end sample in one call
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# SAMPLE_ID and PAIR_ID are used in the curl call
#
# NOTE: get_irida_download_sequence_pair wraps get_irida_download_sequence_file twice.
#
# example: get_irida_download_sequence_pair [TAB for project] 2:Test_Data_Uploading [TAB for sample] 3:sample-1-Added [TAB for pair] 3
